A photorealistic airport terminal scene at dusk, showing a long communal wooden desk near floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking taxiing aircraft on rain-slicked tarmac. Two open laptops sit side by side, their screens glowing warmly, with travelers' hands visible gesturing animatedly in conversation. A steaming cup of green tea, a well-worn passport with colorful visa stamps fanned out beside it, and tangled charging cables create an intimate workspace tableau. The golden hour light filters through the windows, casting long shadows across the polished floor while distant runway lights twinkle like earthbound stars. The mood captures spontaneous human connection amid transit—two strangers sharing knowledge in the liminal space between destinations.
